                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <ul class="uk-list checked-list uk-margin-remove-top uk-margin-remove-bottom uk-hidden@m">
                    <li>Low, fixed monthly fees</li>
                    <li>No hidden charges</li>
                    <li>Secure and simple accountancy software</li>
